title: Drifting Down Under: Part 1
description: Week 1 of our Australia '12 trip...Nick Taylor, Travis Belsito, Ben Horan and Tad Mathews road tripping down the Sunshine Coast, Gold Coast, and through Sydney. Hitting up epic winch spots, glassy rivers, cables, skateparks and beaches along the way.
